long_description: The transparent LifeProof Fre Case helps protect your iPhone 5c from water, dirt, snow and shocks, all while letting your phone's bright color show through. Fre shields your touchscreen under an ultra-flat, optically clear membrane; it's virtually invisible to the eye and touch, and almost invincible to the elements. Anti-reflective optical glass camera lens transforms your iPhone 5c into a colorful waterproof camera; sound enhancement system lets you capture quality audio.
